    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Setup\n\n1. Import this workflow in n8n.\n2. Replace `REPLACE_WITH_PRIVATE_TOKEN` in the Code node with the token used in the Rabbit setup QR.\n3. Configure the Notion credentials in the Notion node.\n4. Replace `REPLACE_WITH_NOTION_DATABASE_ID` with your Notion database ID.\n5. Recommended Notion columns: Name (title), Text (rich text), Source (select), Session (rich text), Input Mode (select), Created (date).\n6. Activate the workflow and use the production webhook URL: `/webhook/rabbit-r1-notion-v0`."
      },
      "id": "ea98f6e2-e0f4-4f2f-9d3e-9a6d9b773f79",
      "name": "Setup note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
